column5: Captured on 09/24 South of Mapleview on 400SB
There's a boat pointing the wrong way?
Boat is not hooked up to my vehicle and following me?  Michael
Why are you in the number 1 lane?
Is that a hands free device????  Boats looking for a new owner. One that will keep it north of 89. LOL

Real curious how it ended up that way???? SUV south of it did not have a hitch.  LOL. That's a 407 transponder & M was driving. I'm in the MV1 directly in front.  Passing slower moving traffic per the HTA   Dash cam wise guy
I would say, the owner that owned it, turned it around, so it would be harder for someone to take it. Steal it.
That sounds like a good guess to me.

Real curious how it ended up that way???? SUV south of it did not have a hitch.   LOL. That's a 407 transponder & M was driving. I'm in the MV1 directly in front.   Passing slower moving traffic per the HTA   Dash cam wise guy That's what I mean, there is no beer can on the dash

When I passed it there were a couple of cars as well as the SUV and a police vehicle there. I went by thinking "Must have a flat or a minor fender bender" then a couple of minutes down the road realized "Hey, the boat was headed the wrong way"
LOL...I was gonna say, you're sitting in the left lane??? Ya beat me!!
Those back trollers take that stuff serious.
Why wouldn't he be in the left lane Maybe I missed something
